        <Parent_String>masking tape [300014836], pressure-sensitive tape [300014834], adhesive tape [300310136], tape (material) [300014685], materials by form [300014611], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
